	<a href="http://www.michaelangier.com/">Michael Angier</a>.&nbsp; The SuccessNet page for Michael Angier.&nbsp; Beside the information on high performance and on managing agreements and commitments, I see that this is also valuable ot look at in terms of how I present myself on the Web.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#85559930">Thursday, December 05, 2002</a></span></div>
<br>
